Progress update: Fix: Remove incorrect OBI_0000070 annotation property declaration in component files

OBI:0000070 ('assay') is a class in OBI but was being incorrectly declared
as owl:AnnotationProperty in bgo-cl-comp.owl and wmbo-cl-comp.owl. This
declaration was also used as a predicate in axiom annotations throughout
both files.

Fix: Replace owl:AnnotationProperty declaration for OBI_0000070 with
oboInOwl:evidence in bgo-cl-comp.owl, and replace all usages of
<obo:OBI_0000070 rdf:resource="..."/> with <oboInOwl:evidence rdf:resource="..."/>
in both files. The wmbo-cl-comp.owl already had oboInOwl:evidence declared,
so only the OBI_0000070 declaration was removed there.

Resolves the issue where CL was punning OBI:0000070 as both a class and
an annotation property, which OWL treats in completely different ways.

